ted with peak-position variance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-028** [T1] Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-014** [T2] Add systemd unit `cypherclaw-sample-capture.service` that runs `sample_capture_daemon.py` with `Restart=always`, dependent on `cypherclaw-jack.service`. (~6h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-015** [T1] Implement TDD-grade test fixtures with canned 1-second audio windows representing each detector branch (silence, footsteps, dishwasher, music, dogs, transient cluster) for fast deterministic CI. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-016** [T1] Wire `SampleSelector` into `cast_planner.select_cast_ids` so when the cast includes `sw_sampler`, a sample is pre-selected for the piece and attached to the cast metadata. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-017** [T1] Per-mode sampler density gates: composer plays `floor(sampler_density * total_phrases) + Bernoulli(sampler_density)` sampler events per piece (clamped 0..total). (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-018** [T1] When a human plays the MIDI keyboard or Theramini for >5 seconds during a song, capture that input phrase to `samples/keyboard/` or `samples/theramini/` with full tagging. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-019** [T1] Sample-aware harmonic planning: when a sample with known `pitch_hz` is selected, transpose to fit the current piece's key by computing the closest in-key root and applying `pitch_transpose_semitones`. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-020** [T1] Add per-mode effects-bus presets: solitary/evening favor more reverb + delay; working_ambience uses minimal effects; storm uses high freeze + heavy comb-B. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-021** [T2] Surface \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"currently sampling X\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"playing sample Y from source Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" in `operator_diagnostics.py` and the face/inkplate display. (~6h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-022** [T1] Composer post-piece hook: write a sample-usage journal entry per piece (which samples played, what transformations, what arc payoff). (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-023** [T1] Implement `metrics::sampler_event_count_per_piece` and `metrics::sampler_library_vs_self_ratio` for the metrics-CI gate. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~36 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 5: Library & CRUD Polish\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-029** [T1] Implement the Event dataclass with score-level, performance-level, reactive-delta, and provenance fields. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-030** [T1] Implement PerformanceIntent per-phrase metadata with arc shape, deviation bounds, tension target, restraint, and call/response role. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-031** [T1] Implement SectionEnvelope with breakpoint functions over tempo_base, density_target, dynamic_plane, brightness, tension_trajectory. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-032** [T1] Define IntentTag enum (build/settle/question/answer/withhold/punctuate) and require every phrase to carry one. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-033** [T1] Define Role enum (ostinato/m