Scoring):** 3 tasks, ~12 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **Sprint 3 (Improvement Engine Hardening):** 10 tasks, ~36 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n - **Sprint 5 (Library & CRUD Polish):** 9 tasks, ~27 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **Sprint 6 (Stretch Goals):** 3 tasks, ~18 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **Sprint 6 (Stretch Goals):** 1 tasks, ~6 hrs\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Total: 40 tasks, ~129 hours**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Total: 33 tasks, ~111 hours**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260425T183959Zd_1777146814.log:658:./sdp/prd-snapshot.md:119:| CCS-025 | Sample-aware harmonic planning: when a sample with known `pitch_hz` is selected, transpose to fit the current piece's key by computing the closest in-key root and applying `pitch_transpose_semitones`. | MUST | T1 | - `sampler_dispatch::transpose_to_key(record, key_name) -> semitones` returns the integer transposition that maps `record.pitch_hz` to the nearest pitch in the current key (B-rooted modes preferred)<br/>- when `record.pitch_confidence < 0.4`, transposition is set to 0 and the sample plays \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"atonally\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" as a texture<br/>- tests verify transposition for known pitch + key combinations, low-confidence pass-through, and edge cases (octave wraps) |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260425T183959Zd_1777146814.log:738:./my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:113:| CCS-025 | Sample-aware harmonic planning: when a sample with known `pitch_hz` is selected, transpose to fit the current piece's key by computing the closest in-key root and applying `pitch_transpose_semitones`. | MUST | T1 | - `sampler_dispatch::transpose_to_key(record, key_name) -> semitones` returns the integer transposition that maps `record.pitch_hz` to the nearest pitch in the current key (B-rooted modes preferred)<br/>- when `record.pitch_confidence < 0.4`, tr