ler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-030** [T1] Add `sampler_density` field (0.0–1.0) to `ArtistMode` with mode-specific values: solitary 0.7, companion 0.25, working_ambience 0.10, evening_reflection 0.65, storm 0.45. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-031** [T1] Register `voice_sampler` character in `character_registry.py` with `voice.synth = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sw_sampler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, `voice.role = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sampler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, default register, and per-mode gain overrides. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-032** [T1] Implement `sw_sampler.scd` granular SynthDef with bufnum, grain-size, density, position-scrub, pitch-transpose, attack/release envelope, and effects-bus send. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n *Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -80,18 +75,16 @@ Sprints are sequential. Tasks within a sprint can run in parallel unless a depen\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-038** [T2] Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-039** [T2] Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-040** [T2] Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\